description: CT3KIT25664BA1339 is a 6GB kit consisting of (3) 2GB DDR3 Desktop modules that operates at speeds up to 1333 MT/s and has a CL9 latency. It is Un buffered and is non-ECC. It conforms to the industry standard UDIMM layout of 240 pins and is compatible with computers that take DDR3 UDIMM memory.
title: Crucial 6GB Kit (2GBx3) DDR3 1333 MT/s (PC3-10600) CL9 Unbuffered UDIMM 240-Pin Desktop Memory CT3KIT25664BA1339
